title: Garden Grows #4
author: Princess Andrea
pages: Ah, the noble art of farming! 🌾 I feel so... earthy. I've planted wheat, and it grows! 🌱
A garden is befitting a princess, don’t you think? It's quite a satisfying endeavor. 🌻
Animals roam about. A pen for them next? Perhaps livestock management can be added to my resume! 🐑
